 rkwood. This meeting is to plan the schedule for the Board for 2026. Monroe
  PTABOA is a Board made up of 3 Monroe County Property Owners that have a b
 ackground in real estate and taxation. \n\nVickey Reeves\, Level II Indiana
  Assessor-Appraiser\n\nPat Bookwalter\, Developer/Builder\n\nDr. C. Kurt Zo
